THE GAME
--------

  'Triangwa' is a Workbench game where the goal is to place tiles
that contain triangles so their contiguous sides are parallel to
those of the triangles on neighbouring tiles. When that happens,
these tiles are then eliminated and you get points according to
the number of removed tiles.

  After a move is made, whatever the result, a new blank tile will
appear on the game board. This tile can be clicked on to reveal
one or two triangles. Just be careful not to let the game board
fill up completely as that would end the game...

  Have fun!

